{"tid":1278762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭到壓力好大","createTime":"2019-07-02T14:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:10:49.000Z","uid":11779,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bef425023add7e56a20d0e08fc00bdf60bae7008","tid":1278762,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"體力消耗好大。朝早返同時係老麥放長輩圖，lunch又airdrop, 放工好攰，連夜晚發夢都係街抗爭，好辛苦，有時返返下工果時對眼有部份係睇唔到野 但過10幾秒又okay返，有時見到個天係咁轉 好暈。我唔知仲可以捱幾耐 想知其他巴絲係點，你地作休安排係點？定我太過投入？定要抖一抖先繼續？？<br />\n<br />\n我認我要生存要交租 我住緊板間房200尺都要7千一個月，我冇可能完全擺工，我都預左要繼續科金去外國登報。<br />\n有時想放棄 但我諗我住200尺要7千 係因為新移民搶晒香港資源，我過緊狗一樣嘅生活係因為冇民選特首，再過幾年我可能連呢個狗屋都冇得住，同天琦佢地比 我啲痛苦又算啲咩？<br />\n想請教其他人點樣取得平衡，謝謝。"},{"pid":"d95ea6471c041244a8ce3dd81ab1564d0fa361a9","tid":1278762,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f6b16d30c52ece384f8475eb6b0efa3ce9bbbb","tid":1278762,"uid":264459,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:21:40.000Z","msg":"比自己抖下<br />\n唔好所有時間精神擺哂落去<br />\n要比自己放鬆下<br />\n睇下劇睇下書休息下無壞<br />\n<br />\n一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14f630faadad89e9d02a4e11cccdbae165da74b","tid":1278762,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"抖下放鬆下先喇,呢場係持久戰黎"},{"pid":"a41ae7a0c8fa598fae455302f399f274f251dc62","tid":1278762,"uid":39021,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:24:01.000Z","msg":"頂唔順就唔好捐錢, 有行動已經好好<br />\n捐錢就留返畀D唔敢行動嘅人做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3118e0f7218d50b267eef9d0a84ffe4884423831","tid":1278762,"uid":162331,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"頂唔順就抖吓先 我哋成班人會頂上<br />\n錢銀又係一個好大嘅問題 我自己都只係個學生 錢就真係出唔到幾多 <br />\n唯有出多幾分力<br />\n但我覺得比起課金 保障到自己日常生活先係最緊<br />\n之後條路可能仲好漫長 身心都要撐落去!!"},{"pid":"fdf36c8a127e8ac3a0a0faa6fba0b217b4d7ece0","tid":1278762,"uid":83283,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"盡自己能力就好了<br />\n我地需要長期抗爭 <br />\n唔希望各位谷爆自己<br />\n不想再有人壓力過大<br />\nching 你如果有經濟困難 <br />\n你airdrop下做下鍵戰都好好了<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"e012febbb61edbfd63f55e50175d7508c47c7ff8","tid":1278762,"uid":204726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"你抖下先啦 仲有我地係度back up<br />\n你已經好叻盡曬力架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533c44cece5d1b24bf92d2ee732f38fc2aaf3ad9","tid":1278762,"uid":41525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:44:52.000Z","msg":"照顧好自己先<br />\n唔洗超越自己能力<br />\n要好好生活見證香港變返東方之珠既一刻<br />\n而且現在係鍵戰既時刻<br />\n你都可以出一分力"},{"pid":"8517260ee93c84318e72f41e35dd034f5cd02c18","tid":1278762,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"抖下啦"},{"pid":"f44615c9fb95e0209c4d6684c195a156e84c89a8","tid":1278762,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"加油呀師兄 你已經做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾日放鬆下 睇下on9野笑下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2769ac5c6ba00525e6a40238acef4d95ef43ac","tid":1278762,"uid":258770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"唔好再上連登住 避開新聞比自己精神休息下<br />\n經濟環境唔好就唔好課金 我地課埋你個份"},{"pid":"a959ee12d39fc43f9f6a3e7c8f518a17a3f22579","tid":1278762,"uid":212318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"抖！"},{"pid":"34192e5fd44b141039a386b520da80833cf27275","tid":1278762,"uid":576